{"tid":1514852,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"白宮聯署簽得返：太多人重開聯署，請集中推呢個「反對曾偉雄」，9月25日截止","createTime":"2019-08-29T02:19:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T17:32:30.000Z","uid":90735,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"3f2b94758de621989d3d61edc56b2e45685277c4","tid":1514852,"uid":90735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T02:19:11.000Z","msg":"之前巴打開post推白宮聯署，點知聯署網站俾黑客攻擊，過咗deadline未夠數，依家有好多人重開<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">太多人重開聯署，請集中推呢個人數最多嘅「反對曾偉雄」</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n如果入過我嘅post而簽咗嘅，請重簽！<br />\n**************<br />\n<strong>請copy 呢段訊息去Whatsapp group廣傳</strong><br />\n<br />\n白宮聯署：請求美國反對前警務處處長曾偉雄<br />\n出任聯合國駐維也納辦事處總幹事之提名<br />\n之前網站受黑客攻擊，以致大量市民無法聯署，過咗deadline未夠數，依家重開<br />\n<br />\n9月25日截止，現時4,072人已簽，要儲齊10萬簽名 (尚欠99,256個簽名)<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/we-demand-rejection-andy-tsangs-nomination-united-nations-positions-4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fwe-demand-rejection-andy-tsangs-nomination-united-nations-positions-4&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTKtywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=749a9fcd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/we-demand-rejection-andy-tsangs-nomination-united-nations-positions-4</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">簽完記得確認返電郵<br />\n唔好開分身簽名，否則check到可能被取消簽名</span></strong>"},{"pid":"8a6957bef5f3ef840ff3cfb08c3b6a2c984c63ee","tid":1514852,"uid":90735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T02:19:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"191e1c08e61a7370ae02236cf15ef26153ee3490","tid":1514852,"uid":90735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T02:19:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2aec7ab0f7341b330e50e3abfee98babec13707","tid":1514852,"uid":90735,"l